<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-06-1027 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper presents the integrated surface independent subsea interventionsystem - Sisis- for subsea production installations and pipelines. Topicscovered include: a manned autonomous load- carrying submarines with roboticwork systems; an integrated template manifold concept for interventionby the submarine; a diverless emergency pipeline repair system for deepwaters.</TEXT></DOC>